<s docid="AP890922-0193" num="26" wdcount="17"> Sept. 17 _ On Antigua, two people are 
killed and there is widespread wind and rain damage.</s>
<s docid="AP890922-0193" num="33" wdcount="10"> At least one person is reported killed 
on St. Croix.</s>
<s docid="AP890922-0193" num="34" wdcount="17"> Early reports say 97 percent of the 
